{
  "stem": "24125.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In terms of the professions in town, what were the jobs or the work that Jews did in your area?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So mainly schools and up until the war and during the war, even.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's later during the war that I had to work very hard physically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's about all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, I did not have any profession really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say [SIGHS] more by Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say a good 80% Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it's my opinion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I might be wrong in the 20 different ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Ostrog?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how healthy because I was too young to understand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jew still was a Jew and a dirty Jew and, and they belong in ghetto and whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And go to Israel, and-- it, it was anti-Semitic atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Stadniki it was our hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We spoke-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We spoke fluently Polish and Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And just because of that, I think it was a big plus for us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every place we went-- like we went to school-- nobody could really detect my Jewish accent.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was accepted faster than anyone with a Jewish accent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had the plus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Ukrainians the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There is not a slight Jewish accent because we spoke it so much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mainly they had their own little houses, little outskirt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they, they were mingling with the Jewish peddlers and selling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I would say their main [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] work was the farms and around the farms, selling everything from the farms and dealing with Jews, of course.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the biggest flea market, I would call it, or market, was, I guess, in Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
